channel.title: [Release]Multi-Code Generator[Release]
channel.description:
[center]I recently finished coding a Code generator for new developers, or any advanced developer that wants to save some time on basic code.
It comes with 5 different generators; Shop, NPC Spawn, NPC Drop, Command, and Item Stat. Each of them has in-depth options to allow full customization of everything.
It was coded with VS 2010 in VB.NET.
[u]Note: Before you start saying "fake" or "omg virus" or anything like that, please bother to actually take the time to scan it and/or try it first.[/u]
[b]Pictures (sorry for the bad quality):[/b]
[img]http://i1220.photobucket.com/albums/dd453/makiener/Generator.jpg[/img]
[img]http://i1220.photobucket.com/albums/dd453/makiener/Generator5.jpg[/img]
[img]http://i1220.photobucket.com/albums/dd453/makiener/Generator2.jpg[/img]
[img]http://i1220.photobucket.com/albums/dd453/makiener/Generator3.jpg[/img]
[img]http://i1220.photobucket.com/albums/dd453/makiener/Generator4.jpg[/img]
[b]V Scans:[/b] [url=http://www.virustotal.com/file-scan/report.html?id=8f2c91aabadc834a4d169d362fe860f752e95dd5bba09f8746b2fe43bac04aa5-1307938702]http://www.virustotal.com/file-scan/report.html?id=8f2c91aabadc834a4d169d362fe860f752e95dd5bba09f8746b2fe43bac04aa5-1307938702[/url] Or [url=http://vscan.novirusthanks.org/analysis/d736bfdc4a3b6a55576656a5de59d2ce/Y29kZS1nZW5lcmF0b3ItZXhl/]http://vscan.novirusthanks.org/analysis/d736bfdc4a3b6a55576656a5de59d2ce/Y29kZS1nZW5lcmF0b3ItZXhl/[/url]
[b]Or scan it yourself:[/b] [url=http://vscan.novirusthanks.org/]http://vscan.novirusthanks.org/[/url] Or [url=http://www.virustotal.com/]http://www.virustotal.com/[/url]
[quote="gnomez"]i decompiled it looked through it a bit it appears to be fine[/quote]
In order to run it, you need .NET Framework 4.0. Get it here: [url=http://www.microsoft.com/net/download.aspx]http://www.microsoft.com/net/download.aspx[/url]
[b]Download:[/b] [url=http://www.mediafire.com/?89g1vz6b2sq75so]http://www.mediafire.com/?89g1vz6b2sq75so[/url]
Also, to any who have seen this post elsewhere, I am Makiener & Ass Kicker. If you don't believe me, you can look for kickass-scape and see it posted under my username.
If you downloaded it and thought it was good, please leave a reply, and I will almost always reply back. If you are a .NET coder and want the source code, PM me and I may give it to you.
Enjoy[/center]
